text: Mozammel Haque is a National Awami Party (Muzaffar) politician and the former Member of Parliament of Brahmanbaria-1. ==Career== Haque was elected to parliament from Brahmanbaria-1 as a National Awami Party (Muzaffar) candidate in 1986 and 1988. ==References== Category:National Awami Party (Muzaffar) politicians Category:Living people Category:3rd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:4th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Mozammel Haque (NAP (Muzzafar) politician)
